Extending the envelope from `04 §4.6.9`:

```text
{
  code: <jsonrpc-or-app-code>,
  message: "...",
  data: {
    app_code: "...",
    category: "...",
    recoverable: <bool>,
    hint: "...",
    context: { ... },
    autoHeal?: {
      cause: "...",
      suggestedActions: [ <pointer>, ... ],
      likelihood: "high" | "medium" | "low",
      requiresUserConfirmation: <bool>
    }
  }
}
```
